-  NSMetadataUbiquitousItemUploadingErrorKey 

Global Variable# NSMetadataUbiquitousItemUploadingErrorKey

iOS 7.0+iPadOS 7.0+Mac Catalyst 13.1+macOS 10.9+tvOS 9.0+visionOS 1.0+watchOS 2.0+

```
let NSMetadataUbiquitousItemUploadingErrorKey: String
```

## [Discussion](/documentation/foundation/nsmetadataubiquitousitemuploadingerrorkey#Discussion)

The value is an [`NSError`](/documentation/foundation/nserror) object that describes the problem that occurred when uploading the item to iCloud failed.
